milestones.description: Vengsarkar's 88 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for IND), surpassing Brijesh Patel's 82
Yashpal Sharma has broken the record for most sixes (5) in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 4
Mike Gatting has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for ENG, going past Graham Gooch's 3
Mike Gatting and David Gower's 110-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 89 between Mike Denness and Chris Old
